name: Etherym Bottomless Maw
text:
You can banish 1 "Etherym" monster from your GY, then target 1 monster on the field; destroy that target. An "Etherym" Xyz monster Xyz Summoned with this card as Xyz Material gains this effect:
? You can detach 2 Xyz Materials from this card (Quick Effect); Destroy 1 monster your opponent controls.
